DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       A  ssttrruucctt  ttaaii  stores  an integer between 0 inclusive and
       2^64 exclusive.  The format of ssttrruucctt ttaaii is  designed  to
       speed  up  common operations; applications should not look
       inside ssttrruucctt ttaaii.

       A ssttrruucctt ttaaii variable is commonly used to  store  a  TAI64
       label.   Each  TAI64  label  refers  to one second of real
       time.  TAI64 labels span a period of hundreds of  billions
       of  years.   See hhttttpp::////ppoobbooxx..ccoomm//~~ddjjbb//pprroottoo//ttaaii6644..ttxxtt for
       more information.

       A ssttrruucctt ttaaii variable may also be used to store the numer-
       ical difference between two TAI64 labels.

